snippet.title: Planetiles - Official Announcement Trailer | Gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
🚀 Planetiles is a serene city-builder about crafting natural habitats on remote planets. Create a space haven, protect it from natural disasters, and evolve your world while completing challenging quests. Craft unique biomes and unlock exciting bonuses and new tile types.

🪐 Wishlist Planetiles on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2447030/Planetiles/

Planetiles is a game developed by MythicOwl and published by The Iterative Collective: 
➡️ https://theiterative.co/ 
➡️ https://mythicowl.com/

➡️ https://twitter.com/planetiles

#Planetiles #Steam #IndieGame #Gamescom2023
